BSC.name: Enrex
BSC.description: Enrex - DeFi gateway to environmental commodities for green energy, CO2 allowances/offsets & tree planting.
BSC.about: Enrex is the DeFi solution to making your crypto operations carbon neutral. Using blockchain, we provide all crypto companies and investors access to carbon offset certificates. The officially recognized environmental commodities can be purchased by companies both in crypto and the real world. This allows users to instantly offset the CO2, created by minting NFTs, mining cryptos, trading, or other activities. Our in-house calculation system automatically counts the amount of CO2 generated and provides you an exact cost to offset it. The application is easily integrated in a variety of systems and can be set up to complete all processes automatically. At the end of every transaction, you are provided with a certificate that unequivocally proves, that your operations are carbon neutral. In addition to this, Enrex: Provides investing opportunities in the growing environmental commodities market. – Our native token - $ENRx, that is used to complete the offsetting process is also available topurchase by the general public. This allows people and companies to invest in a token that is directly connected to the environmental commodities market. Helps launch sustainable and CO2 neutral ICO/IEO/IDOs on any blockchain. We provide solutions and technical assistance to make launches on any blockchain carbon neutral.

BSC.name: Karat DAO IDO

BSC.description: The largest protocol on ZKSync.  Karat has over 300,000 wallets actively transacting. Each user has verified their web3 wallet and their web2 id/behavior data. BSC.about: Karat has received investments from institutions such as Bitmart, NEO Eco, Longling Capital, Emurgo Capital, Milestone Capital, and others. This infrastructure is intended to be the infrastructure of all future Dapps that require Web3 social, data indexing, advertising delivery, and login permission calls.
